,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"貨van 好似踩到6,7 km/h 都未死<br />\n記得有一堂個師傅特登叫我踩break 唔踩離合， 睇下大概幾速先死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"要睇你幾波"},{"pid":"2bc219d852498dd249e3931bb6b0b6fba8ca1032","tid":2384951,"uid":180401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"耍depend 你幾km<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果5km樓下<br />\n你break先 就死火<br />\n<br />\n如果50km 樓下就break 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39774505be990475b2cdced96dbfd91996864f23","tid":2384951,"uid":156573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d62f18b5beb4a4e71c986f71331d36d761170e1d","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣樣，跟咗個教車師傅學棍波車<br />\n本來唔想好似陳百祥咁學個廢牌<br />\n上第一堂佢就教我停車個步驟<br />\n<br />\n1）踩離合<br />\n2）踩break<br />\n3）拉手掣<br />\n4）空波<br />\n5）放腳<br />\n<br />\n我上YouTube先知咁樣叫空波滑行<br />\n其實點樣停車先啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"我講一次<br />\n先用brake 減速<br />\n車速已經好慢，臨停車，踩離合，再加多少少brake完全煞停<br />\nhand brake，空波（check），放腳<br />\n<br />\n上斜停車既話我師傅教離合可以早少少落，但注意落得離合其實你同完全停定既時間點都唔會差得好遠"},{"pid":"895e1388d8d80b4466f918285ad18e3794f61a47","tid":2384951,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"你車速慢，係可以極力子先<br />\n但當然唔係叫你成百米踏<br />\n停車前1，2個車位踏唔計，空波滑行"},{"pid":"4fb50af07c619fa821fcd9b3ada6498c8e4cc591","tid":2384951,"uid":31335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"56563d634043248216e3f510b78f808eb19bfcf7","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":85,"score":-85,"quote":{"pid":"b306eee28963bf3318d28e5e6c1a915cf0936efc","tid":2384951,"uid":191815,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:16:25.000Z","msg":"臨停車先落左腳"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"踩住極力子到停車個位先落break?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"好難幫你喎咁 唔好學車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acb2245cbf786f25080df34cc096bf368a7e33b","tid":2384951,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"你啱<br />\n波都唔好轉呀<br />\n<br />\n轉緊個下都計空波滑行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa7f87429f4c4341051f16b6efffe44e78ce432","tid":2384951,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d62f18b5beb4a4e71c986f71331d36d761170e1d","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣樣，跟咗個教車師傅學棍波車<br />\n本來唔想好似陳百祥咁學個廢牌<br />\n上第一堂佢就教我停車個步驟<br />\n<br />\n1）踩離合<br />\n2）踩break<br />\n3）拉手掣<br />\n4）空波<br />\n5）放腳<br />\n<br />\n我上YouTube先知咁樣叫空波滑行<br />\n其實點樣停車先啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"step2 同3已經令架車停左，點樣滑行呀？"},{"pid":"329a7452f2c13892bd747ad77aa49e5141c2656e","tid":2384951,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"我都學緊車 想問各位大佬要踩幾深逼力先會死火<br />\n唔敢試驚比師傅屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3339825247138279842e19f3109bf59edbc341","tid":2384951,"uid":294427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6446a521a60fcda65911ceaf803c3c3410a9b3b4","tid":2384951,"uid":71657,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:18:09.000Z","msg":"轉師傅啦仲問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"上斜停車咪踩離合先囉"},{"pid":"0db09bd411ea5ca9e623385986234a69a0a85cec","tid":2384951,"uid":33952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印像中冇比油情況下 1波最低速5-8km/h  2波15-18km/h 3波20頭 km/h<br />\n你要喺冇比油嘅情況之下再減慢車速只得兩個選擇<br />\n1.轉低一個波<br />\n2.踩離合器（1波冇得再轉低，冇比油仲踩brake轉數會好低，車頭震到PK好易死火） <br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e9f50aa494ad1e574baf9ccaa5c5b3d418c715","tid":2384951,"uid":92052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c88c62502697f965a0d74774bb063c1fb7f88b9b","tid":2384951,"uid":66049,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62f18b5beb4a4e71c986f71331d36d761170e1d","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣樣，跟咗個教車師傅學棍波車<br />\n本來唔想好似陳百祥咁學個廢牌<br />\n上第一堂佢就教我停車個步驟<br />\n<br />\n1）踩離合<br />\n2）踩break<br />\n3）拉手掣<br />\n4）空波<br />\n5）放腳<br />\n<br />\n我上YouTube先知咁樣叫空波滑行<br />\n其實點樣停車先啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"初初我師傅都係咁教<br />\n因為開頭速度10-20km/h 基本上落離合再踩brake 唔會死火<br />\n<br />\n但出到街講緊係50km/h<br />\n太快落離合會導致暫時空波<br />\n所以師傅叫用brake 踩慢速，接近停車位置一架車位到就落離合，就停就brake 大力啲，最後停定先手掣空波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"就停唔需要brake大力d 除非你斜路<br />\n根本落住少少brake 接近停車時 慢慢落曬離合 部車就會停得好順<br />\n大力brake通常都chok"},{"pid":"953429dc18ff98aaec6411c13f491abaaaf918e6","tid":2384951,"uid":334786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"係駕駛考試入面唔建議用3波停止<br />\n點都要轉2波先好停<br />\n而2波快極有限<br />\n所以你師父咁教係最簡單的"},{"pid":"9335edb988271857f6faf7478fae34fcd4f2b962","tid":2384951,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b369d5571a0a23a139b40c8e962583dff3f2c4","tid":2384951,"uid":156298,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"d62f18b5beb4a4e71c986f71331d36d761170e1d","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣樣，跟咗個教車師傅學棍波車<br />\n本來唔想好似陳百祥咁學個廢牌<br />\n上第一堂佢就教我停車個步驟<br />\n<br />\n1）踩離合<br />\n2）踩break<br />\n3）拉手掣<br />\n4）空波<br />\n5）放腳<br />\n<br />\n我上YouTube先知咁樣叫空波滑行<br />\n其實點樣停車先啱"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:37:25.000Z","msg":"師父冇教錯..<br />\n但如果速度太高, 就加多個 step 0.. 先brak