n踩brake<br />\n拖波到架車好慢就快停<br />\n踩極力子 <br />\n繼續踩brake停定架車 <br />\n拉手制<br />\n入空波<br />\n鬆brake<br />\n鬆極力子"},{"pid":"1635e8fe46246ea0488792ee500bfc49469bf8e0","tid":2384951,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"踩住brake就唔係空波滑行"},{"pid":"813e8ef59da4cae860d576e4d831b1f19de1e223","tid":2384951,"uid":63974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"其實步驟只要分清 印brake（減速）同brake停（踩停）會清晰好多<br />\n<br />\n利申： 1 take棍波"},{"pid":"6c780ada664d2f4d31d31067caa24ac809a7ca16","tid":2384951,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"第一個step就錯喇 先收慢部車 姐係踩brake先<br />\n之後落離合一波立刻摩擦點 brake照踩 <br />\n車就快停定鬆少少brake 離合再抬高 車會停得最唔chok<br />\n之後落brake 踩低離合 空波 手制"},{"pid":"124496925f95c6a8705cc231e7c758099340a2a2","tid":2384951,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"極力子要分階段落<br />\n最開頭踩少少，之後輕輕掂下break<br />\n最後臨停先慢慢落哂極力子<br />\n之後hand break <br />\n空波<br />\n其實係咪你誤會咗點野<br />\n邊有可能咁基本都教錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cba968c08c7d721f52f12955bad6ac764731c45","tid":2384951,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"如果係一開頭就踩盡極力子，而部車又係向前行就係空波滑行<br />\n我都試過幾次<br />\n因為成日停車停到好chok <br />\n係空波滑行就會順啲"},{"pid":"5d6ac18240335f9efb791b84b6e0a8d3f4998bc4","tid":2384951,"uid":57438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"基本上你20 kmh<br />\n兩隻腳都係一齊落<br />\n左腳慢慢去到最深<br />\n右腳慢慢落去 (唔係印到最深呀, 會CHOK 死師傅架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n架車應該喺你極力子踩到最深時<br />\n速度已經0左"},{"pid":"e8d08cf672508932fe0dda32e9d8dc9920787dee","tid":2384951,"uid":89801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫做踩break?"},{"pid":"176216ddf28771a9e971ae9f9099e291de441623","tid":2384951,"uid":225207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"慢車就1,2同步做啦."},{"pid":"077dff6bb5422af7fab0c8a38136a2bcf98083fb","tid":2384951,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"原來香港真係咁多蠢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb2f8b01b618031c723341e9f5b7ba5e0fd2794","tid":2384951,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"雖然樓豬有d搞笑<br />\n但佢都係學神ja<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3a6a9e3ddae4cdc4ebb378fa467cce1cdf493f","tid":2384951,"uid":31863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"咁樣考牌即肥"},{"pid":"00363bc02ca6ebbfb7de030c9b76aa82d7d39a84","tid":2384951,"uid":5497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:15:14.000Z","msg":"踩break收慢，收到咁上下踩離合，停定拉手掣空波放腳"},{"pid":"dab8e87f0528ed6ccd47403845cd723f1ba235a2","tid":2384951,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"我學o個陣係踩brake踩到kick kick下先鬆離合"},{"pid":"c83bdc615f7dd385f559768ed268fa8513144076","tid":2384951,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56563d634043248216e3f510b78f808eb19bfcf7","tid":2384951,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":85,"score":-85,"quote":{"pid":"b306eee28963bf3318d28e5e6c1a915cf0936efc","tid":2384951,"uid":191815,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:16:25.000Z","msg":"臨停車先落左腳"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"踩住極力子到停車個位先落break?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"問過師傅<br />\n<br />\n先印一下break 表示你係準備停車 <br />\n之後等架車慢慢去到想停嘅位<br />\n就到就先踩離合器 <br />\n到左停車位就落break<br />\n<br />\n如果事先冇踩break直接踩離合當空波滑行<br />\n踩左少少break先 之後踩住離合滑過去都得"}]}